categories: Category:Unidentified members of the Ohnaka Gang

nodes.text: A Weequay male served as a member of the Ohnaka Gang, led by another Weequay, the pirate Hondo Ohnaka during the Clone Wars.

This Weequay participated in an operation on Felucia, where the Ohnaka Gang attempted to ransack a local farming community for a highly valuable crop, nysillin. When a scout sent to the village failed to report in, the Weequay reported his absence to Ohnaka.
This pirate was voiced by James Arnold Taylor, who also voices Obi-Wan Kenobi in The Clone Wars TV series.
